msgstr "Spezifischste"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:456
msgid "Load all matching theme styles"
msgstr "Alle passenden Theme-Stile laden"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:458
msgid ""
"By default, only the most specific theme style is loaded. To load all theme "
"styles whose conditions are met, select \"Load all matching theme styles\"."
msgstr ""
"Standardmäßig wird nur der spezifischste Theme-Stil geladen. Um alle Theme-"
"Stile zu laden, deren Bedingungen erfüllt sind, wähle „Alle passenden Theme-"
"Stile laden“."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:465
msgid "Duplicate content"
msgstr "Inhalte duplizieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:472,
#: ../includes/elements/base.php:3418, ../includes/elements/base.php:3422,
#: ../includes/elements/dropdown.php:605,
#: ../includes/elements/dropdown.php:632,
#: ../includes/elements/instagram-feed.php:295,
#: ../includes/elements/nav-menu.php:1487,
#: ../includes/elements/nav-menu.php:1573,
#: ../includes/elements/nav-nested.php:794
msgid "Enable"
msgstr "Aktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:473
msgid "Disable globally"
msgstr "Global deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:474
msgid "Disable for WordPress data"
msgstr "Für WordPress-Daten deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:476
msgid ""
"Duplicate content is available to all users with the %s capability. Use this "
"feature for any post or page to ensure that all relevant WordPress and/or "
"Bricks data is duplicated accurately."
msgstr ""
"Die Funktion zum Duplizieren von Inhalten steht allen Benutzern mit der %s-"
"Berechtigung zur Verfügung. Verwende diese Funktion für beliebige Beiträge "
"oder Seiten, um sicherzustellen, dass alle relevanten WordPress- und/oder "
"Bricks-Daten genau dupliziert werden."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:477
msgid "Filter for more advanced duplicate content rules"
msgstr "Filter für erweiterte Regeln zum Duplizieren von Inhalten"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:484
msgid "Form submissions"
msgstr "Formular-Übermittlungen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:489
msgid "Save form submissions in database"
msgstr "Formular-Übermittlungen in Datenbank speichern"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:522
msgid ""
"Enable form submission access for specific user roles. Edit the user's "
"profile directly to grant access to a specific user."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere den Zugriff auf Formular-Übermittlungen für bestimmte "
"Benutzerrollen. Bearbeite das Benutzerprofil direkt, um einem bestimmten "
"Benutzer Zugriff zu gewähren."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:536
msgid "Reset database table"
msgstr "Datenbanktabelle zurücksetzen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:541
msgid "Delete database table"
msgstr "Datenbanktabelle löschen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:558,
#: ../includes/elements/query-results-summary.php:18
msgid "Queries of the types \"Post\", \"Term\", and \"User\" are supported."
msgstr ""
"Abfragen der Typen „Beitrag“, „Begriff“ und „Benutzer“ werden unterstützt."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:558
msgid "Avoid using in combination with third-party filter plugins."
msgstr ""
"Vermeide die Verwendung in Kombination mit Filter-Plugins von Drittanbietern."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:577
msgid ""
"The query filter database is outdated. Please click \"Regenerate filter "
"index\" button to update it."
msgstr ""
"Die Abfrage-Filter-Datenbank ist veraltet. Bitte klicke auf den Button "
"„Filter-Index neu generieren“, um sie zu aktualisieren."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:583
msgid "Custom fields integration"
msgstr "Integration benutzerdefinierter Felder"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:586,
#: ../includes/elements/filter-base.php:1625
msgid "Provider"
msgstr "Anbieter"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:591,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:603
msgid "Regenerate filter index"
msgstr "Filter-Index neu generieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:592
msgid ""
"Click \"Regenerate filter index\" to regenerate the query filter index for "
"your entire website."
msgstr ""
"Klicke auf „Filter-Index neu generieren“, um den Abfrage-Filter-Index für "
"deine gesamte Website neu zu erstellen."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:592
msgid ""
"Click \"Continue filter index\" to immediately run any remaining/queued "
"filter index jobs instead of waiting for the next WP cronjob."
msgstr ""
"Klicke auf „Filter-Index fortsetzen“, um sofort alle verbleibenden/in der "
"Warteschlange befindlichen Filter-Index-Jobs auszuführen, anstatt auf den "
"nächsten WP-Cronjob zu warten."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:597
msgid "Fix corrupted database"
msgstr "Beschädigte Datenbank reparieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:608
msgid "Continue index job"
msgstr "Index-Job fortsetzen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:627
msgid "Remove all index jobs"
msgstr "Alle Index-Jobs entfernen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:631
msgid ""
"Click this button to remove all index jobs. Useful if your index jobs are "
"stuck due to unknown reasons. You should regenerate the filter index "
"afterwards."
msgstr ""
"Klicke auf diesen Button, um alle Index-Jobs zu entfernen. Nützlich, wenn "
"deine Index-Jobs aus unbekannten Gründen stecken geblieben sind. Du solltest "
"danach den Filter-Index neu generieren."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:634
msgid "Indexing job is stuck?"
msgstr "Indexierungsjob steckt fest?"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:641,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:645,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:652
msgid "Custom breakpoints"
msgstr "Benutzerdefinierte Breakpoints"

#. translators: %s = article link
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:645
msgid "%s are best configured before you start working on your site."
msgstr ""
"%s sollten am besten konfiguriert werden, bevor du mit der Arbeit an deiner "
"Website beginnst."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:656,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1999
msgid "Regenerate CSS files"
msgstr "CSS-Dateien neu generieren"

#. translators: %s = article link
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:669
msgid ""
"Running the %s detects any outdated Bricks data and automatically updates it "
"to the latest syntax."
msgstr ""
"Das Ausführen des %s erkennt veraltete Bricks-Daten und aktualisiert sie "
"automatisch auf die neueste Syntax."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:669
msgid "Converter"
msgstr "Konverter"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:675
msgid "Please create a full-site backup before running the converter."
msgstr ""
"Bitte erstelle ein vollständiges Website-Backup, bevor du den Konverter "
"ausführst."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:681
msgid "Convert \"Container\" to new \"Section\" & \"Block\" elements"
msgstr "„Container“ in neue „Sektion“- & „Block“-Elemente umwandeln"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:686
msgid "Convert element IDs & classes"
msgstr "Element-IDs & -Klassen konvertieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:691
msgid "Add \"position: relative\" as needed"
msgstr "„position: relative“ nach Bedarf hinzufügen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:696
msgid "Entry animation to interaction"
msgstr "Eingangsanimation zur Interaktion"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:709,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:713
msgid "Custom authentication pages"
msgstr "Benutzerdefinierte Authentifizierungsseiten"

#. translators: %s = article link
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:713
msgid ""
"%s allow you to render custom pages for the user login, registration, lost "
"and reset password."
msgstr ""
"%s ermöglichen es dir, benutzerdefinierte Seiten für die Benutzeranmeldung, "
"Registrierung sowie für verlorene und zurückgesetzte Passwörter zu erstellen."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:771
msgid "Registration"
msgstr "Registrierung"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:814
msgid "WordPress authentication page access"
msgstr "Zugriff auf WordPress-Authentifizierungsseite"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:816
msgid "Redirect to custom authentication page"
msgstr "Weiterleitung zu benutzerdefinierter Authentifizierungsseite"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:818,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-system-information.php:67
msgid "Home URL"
msgstr "Start-URL"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:819
msgid "Redirect to specific page"
msgstr "Weiterleitung zu bestimmter Seite"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:823
msgid ""
"Determines what happens when someone visits a default WordPress "
"authentication URL (%s). Only applies when custom pages above have been set. "
"Caution: If hiding default paths, remember your custom page URLs to avoid "
"lockout."
msgstr ""
"Legt fest, was passiert, wenn jemand eine Standard-WordPress-"
"Authentifizierungs-URL (%s) besucht. Gilt nur, wenn oben benutzerdefinierte "
"Seiten festgelegt wurden. Vorsicht: Wenn du Standardpfade verbirgst, merke "
"dir deine benutzerdefinierten Seiten-URLs, um eine Aussperrung zu vermeiden."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:827,
#: ../includes/elements/filter-submit.php:52
msgid "Redirect to"
msgstr "Weiterleiten zu"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:838
msgid ""
"When someone visits a default WordPress authentication URL (%s), they are "
"redirected to this selected page."
msgstr ""
"Wenn jemand eine Standard-WordPress-Authentifizierungs-URL (%s) besucht, "
"wird er zu dieser ausgewählten Seite weitergeleitet."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:843
msgid "Disable custom authentication page bypass"
msgstr "Umgehung der benutzerdefinierten Authentifizierungsseite deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:846
msgid ""
"By default, users can access the default WordPress auth pages by adding %1$s "
"to the URL, bypassing custom authentication pages. Enable this setting to "
"remove this bypass option and always use your custom authentication pages "
"and behavior as set above."
msgstr ""
"Standardmäßig können Benutzer auf die Standard-WordPress-"
"Authentifizierungsseiten zugreifen, indem sie %1$s zur URL hinzufügen und so "
"benutzerdefinierte Authentifizierungsseiten umgehen. Aktiviere diese "
"Einstellung, um diese Umgehungsoption zu entfernen und immer deine "
"benutzerdefinierten Authentifizierungsseiten und das oben festgelegte "
"Verhalten zu verwenden."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:859,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:867,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:908
msgid "User activation"
msgstr "Benutzeraktivierung"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:860
msgid ""
"Send an email to every newly registered user with an activation link that "
"must be clicked to activate their account."
msgstr ""
"Sende eine E-Mail an alle neu registrierten Nutzer/innen mit einem "
"Aktivierungslink, der angeklickt werden muss, um ihr Konto zu aktivieren."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:861
msgid ""
"There is an \"Activation status\" column under \"Users\", where you can "
"manually set the status to active/inactive and resend the activation email."
msgstr ""
"Unter \"Benutzer\" gibt es eine Spalte \"Aktivierungsstatus\", in der du den "
"Status manuell auf aktiv/inaktiv setzen und die Aktivierungs-E-Mail erneut "
"versenden kannst."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:868
msgid ""
"Enable to require user to verify the email after registration through an "
"activation link."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere die Option, dass der/die Nutzer/in seine/ihre E-Mail nach der "
"Registrierung über einen Aktivierungslink verifizieren muss."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:869
msgid ""
"This feature affects all new user registrations, not just those submitted "
"via the Form element."
msgstr ""
"Diese Funktion betrifft alle neuen Benutzeranmeldungen, nicht nur die, die "
"über das Formularelement übermittelt werden."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:874
msgid "Auto login after activation"
msgstr "Automatische Anmeldung nach Aktivierung"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:875
msgid ""
"Enable to automatically log the user in after successful email verification."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere diese Option, um den Benutzer nach erfolgreicher E-Mail-"
"Verifizierung automatisch anzumelden."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:879
msgid "Verification success page"
msgstr "Erfolgsseite der Überprüfung"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:892
msgid "Verification failure page"
msgstr "Seite für fehlgeschlagene Überprüfungen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:947,
#: ../includes/elements/form.php:1315, ../includes/elements/form.php:1487,
#: ../includes/elements/form.php:1506
msgid "From email address"
msgstr "Absender-E-Mail-Adresse"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:952,
#: ../includes/elements/form.php:1322, ../includes/elements/form.php:1495
msgid "From name"
msgstr "Absendername"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:962,
#: ../includes/elements/form.php:1340, ../includes/elements/form.php:1512
msgid "Email content"
msgstr "E-Mail-Inhalt"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:968,
#: ../includes/elements/form.php:1361, ../includes/elements/form.php:1525
msgid "HTML email"
msgstr "HTML-E-Mail"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:978
msgid ""
"Password protection limits access to content on the rendered frontend only. "
"It does not restrict alternative access methods (e.g. REST API). For "
"sensitive data, consider stricter security controls."
msgstr ""
"Der Passwortschutz beschränkt den Zugriff auf Inhalte nur im gerenderten "
"Frontend. Er schränkt alternative Zugriffsmethoden (z.B. REST API) nicht "
"ein. Erwäge für sensible Daten strengere Sicherheitskontrollen."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:988
msgid "Orphaned elements"
msgstr "Verwaiste Elemente"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:993
msgid "Check for orphaned elements on builder save"
msgstr "Auf verwaiste Elemente beim Speichern des Builders prüfen"

#. translators: %1$s: Link to orphaned elements documentation, %2$s: URL parameter
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:998
msgid ""
"Checks for %1$s on builder save to check for orphaned elements. Always "
"checked on load regardless of this setting. Can also be manually enabled by "
"adding %2$s to the builder URL."
msgstr ""
"Prüft auf %1$s beim Speichern des Builders, um verwaiste Elemente zu finden. "
"Wird unabhängig von dieser Einstellung immer beim Laden geprüft. Kann auch "
"manuell aktiviert werden, indem %2$s zur Builder-URL hinzugefügt wird."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1008
msgid "Scan your site for orphaned elements that may cause issues."
msgstr ""
"Scanne deine Website nach verwaisten Elementen, die Probleme verursachen "
"könnten."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1028
msgid "Builder capabilities"
msgstr "Builder-Berechtigungen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1032
msgid ""
"Set up your own capabilities with the exact permissions you want to allow. "
"Then assign it to specific user roles from the \"Builder Access\" dropdown "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Lege deine eigenen Berechtigungen mit genau den Zugriffsrechten fest, die du "
"erlauben möchtest. Weise sie dann bestimmten Benutzerrollen über das "
"Dropdown-Menü „Builder-Zugriff“ unten zu."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1121
msgid "Add new capability"
msgstr "Neue Berechtigung hinzufügen"

#. translators: %s = article link
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1134
msgid ""
"Set %s per user role. To define access for a specific user edit the user "
"profile directly."
msgstr ""
"Lege %s pro Benutzerrolle fest. Um den Zugriff für einen bestimmten Benutzer "
"festzulegen, bearbeite direkt das Benutzerprofil."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1134
msgid "builder access"
msgstr "Builder-Zugriff"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1172
msgid ""
"This user role has %s capability, and therefore full builder access. "
"Effectively overriding this setting."
msgstr ""
"Diese Benutzerrolle hat die Berechtigung %s und damit vollen Builder-"
"Zugriff. Dies überschreibt effektiv diese Einstellung."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1189
msgid "Template screenshots"
msgstr "Template-Screenshots"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1190
msgid ""
"Enable to automatically generate template screenshots on every builder save, "
"view them, and use the bulk generate button in the template manager."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies, um automatisch Template-Screenshots bei jedem Speichern des "
"Builders zu generieren, sie anzusehen und die Schaltfläche zur "
"Massengenerierung im Template-Manager zu nutzen."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1199
msgid "Delete screenshots"
msgstr "Screenshots löschen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1204
msgid "Template manager thumbnail height"
msgstr "Höhe des Template-Manager-Vorschaubilds"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1206
msgid ""
"Set a specific height for your template manager thumbnails in the builder. "
"Thumbnails exceeding this height auto-scroll on mouseover."
msgstr ""
"Lege eine bestimmte Höhe für deine Template-Manager-Thumbnails im Builder "
"fest. Thumbnails, die diese Höhe überschreiten, scrollen beim Überfahren mit "
"der Maus automatisch."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1212,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1217,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1222
msgid "Template thumbnail column"
msgstr "Template-Vorschaubild-Spalte"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1213
msgid ""
"Enable to show the template thumbnail column under %s, displaying the "
"featured image or screenshot."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies, um die Template-Thumbnail-Spalte unter %s anzuzeigen, die "
"das Titelbild oder den Screenshot zeigt."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1229
msgid "Disable default templates"
msgstr "Standard-Templates deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1230
msgid ""
"If no template conditions are set Bricks shows published templates (header, "
"footer, etc.) on the frontend of your site. Select this setting to disable "
"this behavior. Make sure to set template conditions instead."
msgstr ""
"Wenn keine Template-Bedingungen festgelegt sind, zeigt Bricks "
"veröffentlichte Templates (Header, Footer, etc.) im Frontend deiner Website "
"an. Wähle diese Einstellung, um dieses Verhalten zu deaktivieren. Stelle "
"sicher, stattdessen Template-Bedingungen festzulegen."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1235
msgid "Public templates"
msgstr "Öffentliche Templates"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1236
msgid ""
"Enable to make your templates public and viewable by anyone online. Disable "
"to allow only logged-in users to view your templates."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies, um deine Templates öffentlich und für jeden online sichtbar "
"zu machen. Deaktiviere es, um nur eingeloggten Benutzern die Ansicht deiner "
"Templates zu erlauben."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1241
msgid "My templates access"
msgstr "Zugriff auf meine Templates"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1242
msgid ""
"Allow other sites to browse and insert your templates from their template "
"library. Restrict template access via \"Whitelist URLs\" and \"Password "
"Protection\" settings below."
msgstr ""
"Erlaube anderen Websites, deine Templates in ihrer Template-Bibliothek zu "
"durchsuchen und einzufügen. Beschränke den Template-Zugriff über die "
"Einstellungen „Whitelist-URLs“ und „Passwortschutz“ unten."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1246
msgid "Whitelist URLs"
msgstr "Whitelist-URLs"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1248
msgid ""
"Only grant access to your templates to the websites entered above. One URL "
"per line."
msgstr ""
"Gewähre nur den oben eingetragenen Websites Zugriff auf deine Templates. "
"Eine URL pro Zeile."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1254
msgid "Password protect your templates."
msgstr "Schütze deine Templates mit einem Passwort."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1258
msgid "Exclude templates"
msgstr "Templates ausschließen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1280
msgid "Select templates to exclude from remote template access."
msgstr ""
"Wähle Templates aus, die vom Remote-Template-Zugriff ausgeschlossen werden "
"sollen."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1292
