msgstr "Dynamische Datenbezeichnung im Dropdown ausblenden"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1795
msgid "Expand panel when dropdown is visible"
msgstr "Panel erweitern, wenn Dropdown sichtbar ist"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1803
msgid "Global data sync"
msgstr "Globale Datensynchronisation"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1807
msgid "Sync global classes"
msgstr "Globale Klassen synchronisieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1808
msgid ""
"Enable to sync global classes on every builder save between all open builder "
"instances. Useful to avoid overwriting each others changes when multiple "
"people work on the same dataset (e.g. adding, deleting, modifying global "
"classes)."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies, um globale Klassen bei jedem Builder-Speichervorgang "
"zwischen allen offenen Builder-Instanzen zu synchronisieren. Nützlich, um "
"das Überschreiben von Änderungen zu vermeiden, wenn mehrere Personen am "
"gleichen Datensatz arbeiten (z.B. beim Hinzufügen, Löschen, Ändern von "
"globalen Klassen)."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1814
msgid "Global class import manager"
msgstr "Globaler Klassen-Import-Manager"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1819
msgid "Show for class conflicts"
msgstr "Bei Klassenkonflikten anzeigen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1820
msgid "Show for new classes"
msgstr "Bei neuen Klassen anzeigen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1821
msgid "Show for new & conflicting classes"
msgstr "Bei neuen & konfliktreichen Klassen anzeigen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1822,
#: ../includes/elements/nav-menu.php:852,
#: ../includes/elements/nav-nested.php:868
msgid "Never"
msgstr "Nie"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1824
msgid ""
"Control when to show the global classes import manager when pasting "
"elements, importing classes or templates."
msgstr ""
"Steuere, wann der Import-Manager für globale Klassen angezeigt werden soll, "
"wenn Elemente eingefügt, Klassen oder Vorlagen importiert werden."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1830
msgid "HTML & CSS to Bricks"
msgstr "Von HTML & CSS zu Bausteinen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1836
msgid "Enable (confirm on paste)"
msgstr "Aktivieren (beim Einfügen bestätigen)"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1837
msgid "Enable (no confirm on paste)"
msgstr "Aktivieren (keine Bestätigung beim Einfügen)"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1840
msgid ""
"Control automatic conversion of pasted HTML & CSS clipboard content into "
"Bricks elements, global classes, and global variables."
msgstr ""
"Steuere die automatische Umwandlung von aus der Zwischenablage eingefügtem "
"HTML- und CSS-Inhalt in Bricks-Elemente, globale Klassen und globale "
"Variablen."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1845
msgid "Render"
msgstr "Rendern"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1848
msgid "Disable WP REST API render"
msgstr "WP REST API-Rendering deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1851
msgid "Use AJAX instead of WP REST API calls to render elements."
msgstr ""
"Verwende AJAX anstelle von WP REST API-Aufrufen, um Elemente zu rendern."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1852
msgid ""
"Only set if you experience problems with the default rendering in the "
"builder (REST API disabled, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies nur, wenn du Probleme mit dem Standard-Rendering im Builder "
"hast (REST API deaktiviert, etc.)"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1860
msgid "Instant navigation"
msgstr "Sofortige Navigation"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1865
msgid "Enable instant navigation"
msgstr "Sofortige Navigation aktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1866
msgid "Switch between pages & templates without reloading the builder."
msgstr "Wechsel zwischen Seiten und Vorlagen, ohne den Builder neu zu laden."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1876,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1880
msgid "Disable emojis"
msgstr "Emojis deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1881
msgid "Set for better performance if you don't use emojis on your site."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies für bessere Leistung, wenn du keine Emojis auf deiner Website "
"verwendest."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1887,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1891
msgid "Disable embed"
msgstr "Einbettungen deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1892
msgid ""
"Set for better performance if you don't use embeds, such as YouTube videos, "
"on your site."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies für bessere Leistung, wenn du keine Einbettungen wie YouTube-"
"Videos auf deiner Website verwendest."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1898,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1902
msgid "Disable Google Fonts"
msgstr "Google Fonts deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1903
msgid ""
"Set if you don't use Google Fonts or you've uploaded and self-host Google "
"Fonts as \"Custom Fonts\"."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies, wenn du keine Google Fonts verwendest oder du Google Fonts "
"hochgeladen und als „Benutzerdefinierte Schriften“ selbst hostest."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1914,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1918
msgid "Disable lazy loading"
msgstr "Lazy Loading deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1919
msgid "Set if you have problems with Bricks built-in lazy loading."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies, wenn du Probleme mit dem in Bricks integrierten Lazy Loading "
"hast."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1925
msgid "Lazy load offset"
msgstr "Lazy Load Offset"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1932,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1936
msgid "Disable jQuery migrate"
msgstr "JQuery Migrate deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1937
msgid ""
"Set for better performance if you don't run any jQuery code older than "
"version 1.9."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies für bessere Leistung, wenn du keinen jQuery-Code verwendest, "
"der älter als Version 1.9 ist."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1943,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1947
msgid "Cache query loops"
msgstr "Abfrageschleifen cachen"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1948
msgid ""
"Set to improve performance by caching query loops. This is particularly "
"useful when your query loop arguments remain relatively unchanged. For "
"optimal functionality, ensure that server object caching is enabled for "
"persistent caching. Disable this setting if you experience any unexpected "
"query results."
msgstr ""
"Eingestellt, um die Leistung durch Caching von Abfrageschleifen zu "
"verbessern. Dies ist besonders nützlich, wenn die Argumente deiner "
"Abfrageschleife relativ unverändert bleiben. Für eine optimale "
"Funktionalität stelle sicher, dass das Server-Objekt-Caching für "
"persistentes Caching aktiviert ist. Deaktiviere diese Einstellung, wenn du "
"unerwartete Abfrageergebnisse erhältst."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1954
msgid "Disable class chaining"
msgstr "Klassen-Verkettung deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1958
msgid "Disable chaining element & global class"
msgstr "Verkettung von Element- & globaler Klasse deaktivieren"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1967
msgid "CSS loading method"
msgstr "CSS-Lademethode"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1971
msgid ""
"Page-specific styles are loaded inline by default. Select \"External files\" "
"to load required CSS only and to allow for stylesheet caching."
msgstr ""
"Seitenspezifische Stile werden standardmäßig inline geladen. Wähle „Externe "
"Dateien“, um nur die benötigten CSS-Dateien zu laden und das Caching von "
"Stylesheets zu ermöglichen."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2025,
#: ../includes/assets/files.php:706
msgid "Your uploads directory writing permissions are insufficient."
msgstr ""
"Die Schreibberechtigungen für dein Upload-Verzeichnis sind unzureichend."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1981
msgid "Inline styles (default)"
msgstr "Inline-Stile (Standard)"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1982
msgid "External files"
msgstr "Externe Dateien"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1991
msgid "Please click the button below to generate all required CSS files."
msgstr ""
"Bitte klicke auf den Button unten, um alle erforderlichen CSS-Dateien zu "
"generieren."

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1995
msgid ""
"WP-Cron is disabled on this site. Make sure a server cron job is configured, "
"otherwise scheduled external CSS file generation will not run."
msgstr ""
"WP-Cron ist auf dieser Website deaktiviert. Stelle sicher, dass ein Server-"
"Cron-Job konfiguriert ist, da sonst die geplante Erstellung externer CSS-"
"Dateien nicht ausgeführt wird."

#. translators: %s = human-readable date
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2013,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2949
msgid "Last generated"
msgstr "Zuletzt generiert"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2018
msgid "CSS files processed"
msgstr "CSS-Dateien verarbeitet"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2037
msgid "Webfont loading method"
msgstr "Webfont-Lademethode"

#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:2038
